#: resources/data/hints.ini: [hint:Chamber temperature]
msgid ""
"Chamber temperature\n"
"Did you know that Orca-Flashforge supports chamber temperature?"
msgstr ""
"仓温\n"
"您知道吗？Orca-Flashforge支持仓温。"

#: resources/data/hints.ini: [hint:Calibration]
msgid ""
"Calibration\n"
"Did you know that calibrating your printer can do wonders? Check out our "
"beloved calibration solution in Orca-Flashforge."
msgstr ""
"校准\n"
"您知道吗？校准您的打印机可以带来奇迹？在Orca-Flashforge中查看我们的备受欢迎的"
"校准解决方案。"

#: resources/data/hints.ini: [hint:Auxiliary fan]
msgid ""
"Auxiliary fan\n"
"Did you know that Orca-Flashforge supports Auxiliary part cooling fan?"
msgstr ""
"辅助风扇\n"
"您知道吗？Orca-Flashforge支持辅助部件冷却风扇。"

#: resources/data/hints.ini: [hint:Air filtration]
msgid ""
"Air filtration/Exhaust Fan\n"
"Did you know that Orca-Flashforge can support Air filtration/Exhaust Fan?"
msgstr ""
"空气过滤/排气扇\n"
"您知道吗？Orca-Flashforge可以支持空气过滤/排气扇。"

#: resources/data/hints.ini: [hint:How to use keyboard shortcuts]
msgid ""
"How to use keyboard shortcuts\n"
"Did you know that Orca-Flashforge offers a wide range of keyboard shortcuts "
"and 3D scene operations."
msgstr ""
"如何使用键盘快捷键\n"
"您知道吗？Orca-Flashforge提供了广泛的键盘快捷键和3D场景操作。"

